Accessibility Namespace

In this Article

The Accessibility and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) accessibility interface.

Introduction

For more information about Accessibility, see the Microsoft Active Accessibility documentation in the MSDN library at http://msdn.microsoft.com/library.

Classes

CAccPropServicesClass

The CAccPropServicesClass and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) IAccPropServices interface.
